edu.ucsb.cs56.pconrad.parsing.syntax

Class DefaultASTFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucsb.cs56.pconrad.parsing.syntax.DefaultASTFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTFactory

    public class DefaultASTFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements ASTFactory
    Default implementation of the ASTFactory interface. This is used in the test suites to create ASTs in a manner which is decoupled from the actual AST constructors.
